{"tid":1106611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[全城中伏] 原來1947年已經有人預言marvel 拍Avenger 係為左幫香港政府同中共維穏","createTime":"2019-04-14T16:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T09:51:32.000Z","uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74b3fb91e336e1574902b53f98546d879eda55f7","tid":1106611,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"According to Theodor Adorno in his book &quot;dialectic of enlightenment&quot; published in 1947, he saw film as almost analogous to Marx saw religion, what he famously called the &quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">sign of a oppessed creatures</span></strong>&quot;, &quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">the heart of aheartless world</span></strong>&quot;, and &quot;t<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">he soul of a souless condition</span></strong>&quot;, &quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">The opium of the masses</span></strong>&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nAdorno saw the film industry as a<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> mass organized machine designed to salve the masses</span></strong> and to keep them <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">obedient</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to Adorno, amusement always means putting things out of minds. At its root, is powerlessness, it is indeed escape but not as it claim, escape from bad reality <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">but from the last thought of resisting that reality</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人全城中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f4febb9b9247c4b012cba31ee2b3d32a943a3f","tid":1106611,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8a4c3e2